<script>
$(document).ready(function () {
if ($('#hdnNotesEnabled').val() == 'true') {
$("#btnAddNotes").click(function (e) {
NotesAction(e, "Upsert");
});
$("#btnClearNotes").click(function (e) {
NotesAction(e, "Delete");
});
$("#txtVehicleNotes").on("input", function () {
toggleAddNotes();
});
}
});
function ShowNotes(inventoryId, tenant, auctionLaneId) {
$('#vehicleNotesPopup').modal('show');
$("#txtVehicleNotes").val($("#notes-" + inventoryId.split("~")[0]).val());
$("#notesTenant").val(tenant);
$("#notesInventoryId").val(inventoryId);
$("#notesAuctionLaneId").val(auctionLaneId);
if ($("#txtVehicleNotes").val().toString().trim() != "") {
$("#hAddHeader").hide();
$("#hUpdateHeader").show();
}
else {
$("#hAddHeader").show();
$("#hUpdateHeader").hide();
}
toggleAddNotes();
}

function NotesAction(e, action) {
var params = {
inventoryId:$("#notesInventoryId").val(),
tenant:$("#notesTenant").val(),
notes:$("#txtVehicleNotes").val(),
auctionId:$("#notesAuctionLaneId").val()
};
var baseUrl = window.location.protocol + "//" + window.location.hostname + (window.location.port ? ':' + window.location.port : '');
$.ajax({
type: 'POST',
url: baseUrl + '/VehicleDetail/' + (action == 'Upsert' ? 'AddNotes' : 'DeleteNotes'),
cache: false,
data: (params),
success: function (response) {
if (response.userLoginStatus == false) {
$('#vehicleNotesPopup').modal('show');
}
else {
let inventoryId = params.inventoryId.split("~")[0];
$('#vehicleNotesPopup').modal('hide');
if (action == 'Upsert') {
$("#pdNotesAdd-" + inventoryId).hide();
$("#pdNotesUpdate-" + inventoryId).show();
$('#notes-' + inventoryId).val(params.notes);
// watch stock if not already
let watchElementSelector = "a[watchInventoryId='" + params.inventoryId + "']";
let element = $(watchElementSelector).first();
if (!element.hasClass('is-watching')) {
element.click();
}
}
else {
$("#pdNotesAdd-" + inventoryId).show();
$("#pdNotesUpdate-" + inventoryId).hide();
$("#txtVehicleNotes").val('');
$('#notes-' + inventoryId).val('');
}
}
},
error: function (error) {
$('#vehicleNotesPopup').modal('show');
}
});
}
function toggleAddNotes() {
if ($("#txtVehicleNotes").val() == "") {
$('#btnAddNotes').attr('disabled', 'disabled');
$('#btnClearNotes').attr('disabled', 'disabled');
$('#btnClearNotes').addClass("disable-link");
}
else {
$('#btnAddNotes').removeAttr('disabled');
$('#btnClearNotes').removeAttr('disabled');
$('#btnClearNotes').removeClass("disable-link");
}
}

localStorage['GBPMyVehiclesQuery'] = GBPMyVehiclesQuery;
}
//SetGBPVDISessionObjectSearch();
});

function AddDelWatch(item, InventoryID, BranchNumber, auctionDateTime, auctionLaneId) {
var WatchStatus;
var elementid = "#" + item.id;
if (!$(elementid).hasClass("is-watching")) {
WatchStatus = false;
}
else {
WatchStatus = true;
}
var params = {
watchStatus: WatchStatus,
inventoryId: InventoryID,
branchNumber: BranchNumber,
auctionId: auctionLaneId,
auctionDateTime: auctionDateTime

};
var baseUrl = window.location.protocol + "//" + window.location.hostname + (window.location.port ? ':' + window.location.port : '');
$.ajax({
type: 'POST',
url: baseUrl + '/Vehicles-Auctions/WatchListClick',
cache: false,
data: (params),
success: function (response) {
if (response.userLoginStatus == false) {
window.location.href = "/MyVehicles?FilterValue=W";
}
else {
if ($(elementid).hasClass("is-watching")) {
$(elementid).removeClass("is-watching");
}
else {
$(elementid).addClass("is-watching");
}
if ($('is-watching').length == $('input#hdnItemIdForWatch').length) {
$('#btnWatchItems').addClass('is-watching');
}
}
},
error: function (error) {
}
});
}

$(document).ready(function () {
$('#PlaceBidPopup').on('shown.bs.modal', function (e) {

});
$('.js-back-top').on('click', function () {
$("html, body").animate({ scrollTop: 0 }, 500);
});

var x = document.getElementById("FacetsContainer");
var y = document.getElementById("revealFacetsContainer");

if (getCookie("facetPanelStatus") == 'closed') {
x.style.display = "none";
y.style.display = "block";
} else {
x.style.display = "block";
y.style.display = "none";
}

});

function setCookie(cname, cvalue, exdays) {
const d = new Date();
d.setTime(d.getTime() + (exdays * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000));
let expires = "expires=" + d.toUTCString();
document.cookie = cname + "=" + cvalue + ";" + expires + ";path=/";
}
function getCookie(cname) {
let name = cname + "=";
let decodedCookie = decodeURIComponent(document.cookie);
let ca = decodedCookie.split(';');
for (let i = 0; i < ca.length; i++) {
let c = ca[i];
while (c.charAt(0) == ' ') {
c = c.substring(1);
}
if (c.indexOf(name) == 0) {
return c.substring(name.length, c.length);
}
}
return "";
}
function myFunction() {
var x = document.getElementById("FacetsContainer");
var y = document.getElementById("revealFacetsContainer");

if (x.style.display === "none") {
setCookie("facetPanelStatus", "open", 30);
x.style.display = "block";
y.style.display = "none";
} else {
setCookie("facetPanelStatus", "closed", 30);
x.style.display = "none";
y.style.display = "block";
}

}

</script>
